NOTE: in ipv6 link-local == APIPA in ipv4 

 creat Eui(Extended uniq identifire) by using the mac address of the device
its 64 bit 

Eui created by adding fffe at the middle of mac address 



link-local created by adding fe80: at the frist of Eui and add zeros 


and continue like the last video


----this methodes work in linux and cisco 
not work in windows as it generate random ipv6

